'''CRUD operations with mongoDB'''

How to create Database?
use Databasename

How to create collections?
db.createCollection('collection_name')

How to delete collections?
db.collection_name.drop()

How to delete database?
db.dropDatabase()

                 ```INSERT QUERY````
db.collection_name.insertOne({name:'john'age:23,status:'active'})
db.collection_name.insertMany([{},{},{}])


                 ````FIND`````
db.collection_name.find({age:21})
db.collection_name.find({age:{$gte:21}}) //in between the condition
db.collection_name.find().sort({name:1})//ascending order
db.collection_name.find().sort({age:-1})//descending order
db.collection_name.find().limit(2)//display 2 entries on screen

          `       ```UPDATE`````
db.collection_name.updateOne({name:'Harry'},{$set:{status:'active'}})
db.collection_name.updateMany({age:{$gte:21}},{$set:{status:'very active'}})

                ````DELETE````
db.collection_name.deleteOne({name:'John'})
db.collection_name.deleteMany({status:'active'})


